VW went to a August -> July model year beginning in August, 1955 for the
'56 model year.

Although, it didn't always start in August...

I'm pretty sure October, '57 is a 1958 model.

A breakdown of VIN# vs. month/year on my site:
http://thesamba.com/vw/type2/information/chassisdating.htm

Your Bus might have taken a little longer to build, but not much, only th=
e
Ambo divider would be special, they did sunroof Buses daily.  If the othe=
r
Bus is a Westy, it definately took longer since it went to Westfalia on
the way...

